"<h1>頁面源代碼</h1>\n\n<div class=\"page-source\">\n\t[[include <a href=\"/component:scp-meta-title-hiding\">component:scp-meta-title-hiding</a> css-style=classic]]<br />\n<br />\n[!--<br />\nNOTICE TO TRANSLATORS<br />\n<br />\nTo generate a list of links to all pages that SCP-3939 uses, please paste the following into any page on the wiki:<br />\n<br />\n[[module ListPages category=&quot;fragment&quot; parent=&quot;scp-3939&quot; order=&quot;created_at&quot; perPage=&quot;250&quot;]]<br />\n%%title_linked%%<br />\n[[/module]]<br />\n<br />\nA spreadsheet is available which contains the entire story in a format which may be better for your needs. Please contact me (Croquembouche) if you need it.<br />\n<br />\nWhen re-creating this SCP, for example for translation purposes, it is of utmost importance that the pages are created in the right order - starting with number 0, and ending with number 66.<br />\n<br />\nThank you.<br />\n<br />\nSCP-3939 begins below.<br />\n--]<br />\n<br />\n[[module CSS]]<br />\n:root { --swatch-primary: 187, 0, 17; }<br />\n.story {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;clear: both; border: 3px black solid; padding: calc(20px - 1em) 0 20px 0;<br />\n}<br />\n.story p {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;<br />\n}<br />\n.choices {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;clear: both;<br />\n}<br />\n.choices a {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 30px; border: 1px solid #b01; border: 1px solid rgb(var(--swatch-primary)); border-right: 1px solid transparent; line-height: 30px; position: relative; background: white; z-index: 8; margin-bottom: 0.5em; float: left; clear: both; padding-left: 7px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px<br />\n}<br />\n.choices a::before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;content: &quot;&quot;; position: absolute; border: 16px solid transparent; border-left: 16px solid #b01; border-left: 16px solid rgb(var(--swatch-primary)); right: -33px; top: -1px; z-index: 6;<br />\n}<br />\n.choices a::after {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;content: &quot;&quot;; position: absolute; border: 15px solid transparent; border-left: 15px solid white; right: -31px; top: 0; z-index: 7;<br />\n}<br />\n.choices p {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;clear: both; height: 30px; margin: 0 0 0 0;<br />\n}<br />\n.footer-wikiwalk-nav {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-top: 50px;<br />\n}<br />\n.footer-wikiwalk-nav a:nth-of-type(2) {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;color: black !important;<br />\n}<br />\nspan, a {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;word-break: normal !important;<br />\n}<br />\n@media (max-width: 580px) {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;.choices a {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;line-height: initial !important; margin-left: 10px !important; margin-right: 30px !important;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br />\n}<br />\n[[/module]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/info:start\">info:start</a>]]<br />\n原文：[http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3939 SCP-3939] (//[編號保留；有待研究人員]//)<br />\n作者：[[*user Croquembouche]]<br />\n致謝：[[*user Baseplate-Actual]], [[*user taylor_itkin]], [[*user Tanhony]], [[*user MayD]]<br />\n譯者：[[*user Frederica Bernkastel]]<br />\n<br />\n這是一篇抉擇的故事。每頁底端的箭頭狀超連結將會把你帶到另一頁去。本SCP文本閱讀流程約15分鐘。並無二次閱讀的準備內容。<br />\n[[[cone|作者頁]]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"/info:end\">info:end</a>]]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[[module ListPages category=&quot;fragment&quot; parent=&quot;.&quot; limit=&quot;1&quot; order=&quot;created_at&quot; offset=&quot;@URL|0&quot;]]<br />\n%%content%%<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;footer-wikiwalk-nav&quot;]]<br />\n[[=]]<br />\n&lt;&lt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[[[SCP-3938]]] | [/fragment:scp-3939-[[#expr (%%index%%-1)]] SCP-3939] | [[[SCP-3940]]] &gt;&gt;<br />\n[[/=]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n[[/module]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:license-box\">:scp-zh-tr:component:license-box</a><br />\n|author=Croquembouche<br />\n]]<br />\n=====<br />\n&gt; **Name:** Gramophone<br />\n&gt; **Author:** Michael Bußmann<br />\n&gt; **License:** CC0<br />\n&gt; **Source Link:** https://pixabay.com/photos/gramophone-turntable-shellac-disc-1790007/<br />\n&gt; **Additional Notes:** Released in 2016<br />\n=====<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:license-box-end\">:scp-zh-tr:component:license-box-end</a>]]\n</div>\n"